Goal: Verify direct Azure AD OIDC integration with GKE Identity Service.

Phases:
  - Run setup: install all dependencies and bootstrap Backstage app
  - Local sandbox with Kind + Dex (mock Azure AD)
  - Deploy Backstage (Azure OIDC) + Headlamp plugin
  - Validate Azure AD tokens accepted by GKE
  - Validate RBAC through Headlamp UI

Success Criteria:
  - Login via Backstage succeeds.
  - Headlamp forwards Bearer token to GKE.
  - GKE authenticates via Azure AD issuer.
  - RBAC enforced as defined for each user.
